reviewText: DEHYDRATOR DELIGHTS,, IS JUST THAT A DELIGHT!!!
I have never given a bad review to any book or DVD, however this was a total waste of money and I really did not learn anything.

I learned a lot about the value of dehydrating your food! It included lots of information about what kind of dehydrator to use, tons of recipes, and all the many kinds of foods you can dehydrate. Yes, fresh and organic is best, but dehydrating those foods, so you can eat them year round is the next best thing! I can't wait to try out some of the recipes! Yummy!
